data.description: Step into a spacious and airy open-concept layout, where the living, dining, and kitchen areas flow seamlessly together.  Descend into the expansive basement family room, ideal for movie nights, game days, or simply unwinding with loved ones. With plenty of space for lounging and entertaining, this versatile area offers endless possibilities. Host unforgettable gatherings on the expansive deck. Needing storage? The basement has a large storage room. If you are needing a to work from home, this home has a large office with French doors.   Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from county records .  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
